
<h1>What is Chai?</h1>

<p>Chai is a simple way to quickly find a nice coffee shop nearby you. If you're like one of the many
  telecommuters who live and work around the city, you know that it can be difficult finding a good local
  shop that is accommodating. Chai is the solution to that.</p>

<br />

<h1>How do I use Chai?</h1>

<p>It's easy! Sign up for your free account. Once you are logged in, click the "Find a nice place to work"
  button, and Chai will automatically find your location and point you to locations that are within your
  vicinity.</p>

  <br />

<h1 style= "margin-bottom: 15px;">What technologies is Chai built with?</h1>

<p>Chai is built using Ruby on Rails, HTML, CSS, Javascript, JQuery, AJAX.<p>

<br />
<h1>Who is the team behind Chai?</h1>

<p>Chai was conceived and created by four software engineers who know the difficulty in finding a good place to work. Like many engineers,
  they like being able to sit down at a coffee shop with a nice atmosphere, fast WIFI, plenty of outlets, and of course, good coffee.
</p>

